{"id": 7313, "title": "Ticket #7313: WeightedIdleJob in submitter ad needs to be a float", "description": "<blockquote>\nDESY reports that they thousands of idle jobs in a schedd.  Submitter ads for these user show up in the collector, but have 0 demand.  Turns out the slot_weight in the schedd is a floating point: 0.5 * cpu + memory / 2048, which is rounding down to zero for all the jobs.  This is because the schedd treats each value as an int.  Let's promote this to a double.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<em>2019-Oct-21 13:08:35 by tim:</em> <br/>\n\n<strong>CODE REVIEW</strong>: Looks good</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Oct-22 09:27</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58226\">[58226]</a></span>: Document <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7313'); return false;\" title=\"WeightedIdleJob in submitter ad needs to be a float\">#7313</a></span>  (By Greg Thain )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2019-Oct-09 17:19</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=58065\">[58065]</a></span>: Make <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=WeightedJobsIdle\" title=\"Weighted Jobs Idle\">WeightedJobsIdle</a></span> a double, not an int <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=7313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('7313'); return false;\" title=\"WeightedIdleJob in submitter ad needs to be a float\">#7313</a></s